
<div class="relative overflow-hidden bg-yellow-100">
  <div class="relative pt-6 pb-16 sm:pb-24">
    <div>
      <nav class="relative mx-auto flex max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6" aria-label="Global">
        <div class="flex flex-1 items-center">
          <div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between md:w-auto">
            <a class="text-yellow-900 font-bold text-2xl" href="#">
              I Owe You
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <%= form_for( :user, url: { action: "login", controller: "users" }, :html => {:class => 'flex' }) do |form| %>
        
          <%= form.label :email, :class => "sr-only" %>
          <%= form.text_field :email, class: "rounded-md border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:border-yellow-500 focus:ring-yellow-500 sm:text-sm mr-5", placeholder: "Your email" %>

          <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md border border-transparent bg-yellow-300 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-yellow-900 hover:bg-yellow-400 ">Log in</a>
        
        <% end %>
      </nav>

    </div>

    <main class="mt-16 sm:mt-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
        <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
          <div class="px-4 sm:px-6 sm:text-center md:mx-auto md:max-w-2xl lg:col-span-6 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:text-left">
            <div>
              <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-yellow-800 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">Effortlessly track obligations between friends</h1>
              <p class="mt-3 text-base text-yellow-700 sm:mt-5 sm:text-xl lg:text-lg xl:text-xl">Quickly record IOUs so you don't forget to pay your friend back (or he doesn't forget to pay you back). Double confirm so you're both on the same page and track the fulfillment of each obligation. Track any obligation, not just money, owe your friend a carwash? You can record that.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-16 sm:mt-24 lg:col-span-6 lg:mt-0">
            <div class="bg-yellow-200 sm:mx-auto sm:w-full sm:max-w-md sm:overflow-hidden sm:rounded-lg">
              <div class="px-4 py-8 sm:px-10">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-yellow-700">Create an IOU</p>

                <div class="mt-3">
                  <%= render :partial => "deals/form" %>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="border-t-2 border-gray-200 bg-yellow-50 px-4 py-6 sm:px-10">
                <p class="text-xs leading-5 text-yellow-500">By submitting this data, you agree to our <a href="#" class="font-medium text-yellow-900 hover:underline">Terms</a>, <a href="#" class="font-medium text-yellow-900 hover:underline">Data Policy</a> and <a href="#" class="font-medium text-yellow-900 hover:underline">Cookies Policy</a>.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>
</div>
